Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上…好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是我来太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像谁都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抖S属性越来越得心应手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不可抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那里做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚深夜动画看多了 现在好困
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.33,0:02:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是喜欢动画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 日本的美少女动画最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意大利那边没有动画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是有的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面没有黑发的日本女性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您这要求…有点高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我对外国的动画很感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐真的很喜欢外国呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有什么契机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:23.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5岁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲带来的客人 是第一次见到的外国人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就对外国感兴趣了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我也正好对日本有些腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5岁就对自己的国家腻了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家从前起 和风就比较重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以当我看到父亲招待的外国人时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间就被外国的魅力所俘虏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像小孩子在场会打扰他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被赶了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后还有因为太向往外国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:17.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想把头发染成金色的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把头发染成金色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.65,0:04:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要因为自己眼神凶恶就放弃治疔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放弃 一定会有更好的路的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被父母全力阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还拼命地鼓励了我一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都因为自己太喜欢国外 给父母添了少麻烦，
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我直到现在都还在反省、
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我太喜欢炸鸡爷爷的人像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一整天都死死盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 多好的故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的…初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人像是初恋什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是小时候真的好喜欢好喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一整天都盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就给父母添了麻烦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.25,0:05:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说有个孩子一直盯着人像 添了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是店家联系了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我又认识了圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便追着父母求他们在家里装烟囱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整整求了一年365天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都求？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…我无论如何都想逮住圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 在和风建筑里弄个烟囱是很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.74,0:05:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐 你刚才说要逮住…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐对海外文化的热情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小时候也十分惊人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 说了这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这应该是店长先生的休息时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到莓香小姐的故事 我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我光顾着说自己的事 害店长削减了睡眠时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么道歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来膝枕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想睡个觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把我的大腿当做枕头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐的膝枕什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对我的腿有什么不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Amore
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请容在下享用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的大腿上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有金发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的莓香小姐 太大胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过几年 也会长出一脸白胡子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋月 110
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是你情我愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你情我愿？骗谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要真跟你说的那样 那就拿出证据来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膝枕完之后 脚都发麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这种东西该怎么拿出证据啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都不相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是在骚扰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无缘无故的被误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那触感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.05,0:08:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎样才能正常地跟莓香小姐那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有那种
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让莓香小姐高兴的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.68,0:08:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要准备好那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到莓香小姐喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 海外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.77,0:08:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋月 我想去海外旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以拜托你看店一个月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少扯淡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就先找可以在日本做的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这周周日 要不要和我一起去一家新开的咖啡厅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡厅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没做什么能让您请我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你工作十分努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想感谢你每天的辛勤付出…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢店员的努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一种慰劳会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.16,0:09:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必让我参加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那周日早上八点半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在涉谷的八公前碰头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和莓香小姐约会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深夜动画看完了都还睡不着觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 没想到你有这意图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香跟我们说 店长要犒劳我们一番
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过星川倒是很敏锐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口就拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟的女性还是不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法少女Frill 即将播出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.17,0:10:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说可能是偏见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为意大利的男性早习惯了这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.55,0:10:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会十分娴熟地处理的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真的是偏见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我是十分敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会做出大胆的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是个胆小鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你不是经常和店里以及路上碰到的女性谈笑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.61,0:10:51.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔接待女性是绅士的原则
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别自称绅士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.66,0:10:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你对樱之宫拿出绅士那套不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:11:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能用面对路人的态度去面对莓香小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你绅士原则去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长 我们今天会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要帮忙倒是可以 但怎么帮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.93,0:11:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要做一些能让女孩子心动不已的事就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在约会的时候上缴贡品是基本中的基本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那叫礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 莓香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去咖啡厅之前能先一起购物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在这里买到适合莓香小姐的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.67,0:11:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拜托二位讲解了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 只在网上买过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐你喜欢什么样的衣服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 秋月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给点建议啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.53,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且说起这一带的店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问客人您需要些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被您发现那条裙子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超可爱的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然自己工作也这么做的 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于生活在不同世界的我们实在太刺激了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不也同样是服务业的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,类型差太多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很受欢迎的 进货之后马上就卖完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易赶上重新进货的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以客人您非常幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也有条不同色的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害的接客能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一提 那条裙子搭上这件上衣是现在的爆款
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么想要的搭配吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以给您指点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.62,0:13:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不能再继续麻烦人家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.09,0:13:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还有什么需要的请叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香 好强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐 你有什么想要的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边的衣服太花哨了 似乎没有适合我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.48,0:13:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.56,0:13:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个玩偶的钥匙扣怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个耳朵的形状 这个突出的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有还有 这个手感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想把这个挂在背包上面对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你很喜欢那个钥匙扣呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处转了个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐完全不给机会让人送礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆强行送一件礼物给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不收的话就硬塞进她的包里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香 你去哪了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我有件东西想给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真巧呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也有想给店长先生的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.71,0:14:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长非常想要的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是您带我到处逛的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在刚才那个店里买的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这也是你陪我到处逛的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就凑一对了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香好口爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长先生 流鼻血了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是客人落下的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 莓香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人落下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别丢在地上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 不过是同人志而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没满十八岁 不能让你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人忘记的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:15:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在被称为是梦幻的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带赠品的卷帘门前社团的花丛文件的会场限定版同人志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去可不是花丛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们说这些 好让人在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.14,0:16:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 莓香你看到了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什么样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子 衣服 捆绑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是在流汗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 不用说也没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这个忘记的东西该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会回来取的 那之前先保管着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了许多人点餐 可以先回来下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息休息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.40,0:17:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这工口JK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是只有我一个人没看过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好让人在意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:17:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「只有我」这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香那是不可抗力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香要和这本书保持那么远的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莓香你在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没来取走么 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一直放着对我太不友好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在意着 都没法集中精神工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不好擅自处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.91,0:18:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不干脆和所有客人都问一下怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢 你是要直接问那本书的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用只有当事人才知道的方式间接去问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这季那个动画超有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我周围也都是这个的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 恕我冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们喜欢被绑起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我问得再间接一点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:22.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西馆和东馆连通处会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有对水手服女生这样那样的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是比刚才间接了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉大概明白那本书的内容了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.47,0:19:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贴上失物招领的公告再多等一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失物招领 书
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太笼统了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没法直接写呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 今天已经结束营业了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天我好像是在这里忘记把书带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么漂亮的女生居然是那本书的…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 是什么样的书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,标题是「与我一起捆绑到尽头 强硬my way」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了是绑起来的那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.38,0:20:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不用说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.89,0:21:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢书的人来取走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.02,0:21:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好贴了公告呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真没想到会是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是女性客人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近真的多了好多时髦的宅女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔还会有些跟模特似的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.53,0:21:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也经常会去同人活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会买各种同人志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「各种」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还以为一定会是男的呢
